Overlap warnings
World soul vs human soul: keep world soul essay cosmological; keep human soul essay existential/practical.
Time vs astrology: time essay should explain cosmic temporality; astrology essay should come later with Ficino/Greenbaum.
Chōra vs imaginal realm: do not flatten chōra into “imagination.” Treat it as matrix of becoming, then cautiously compare.
Geometry vs alchemy: Plato gives mathematical elemental structure, not Renaissance alchemy yet. Alchemical bridges belong in later comparative essays.
