Keep separate:

Cave as cosmos and two gates. The cave is the world-structure; the gates are the soul’s directional transit.
Bees/honey and nymphs/water. Both are “natural” symbols, but bees are soul/purity/ritual; nymphs are watery generation.
Athena’s olive tree and Odysseus’ return. Athena is guiding intellect; Odysseus is the soul being guided.

