Keep separate:

Aerial substance and messenger function. One is ontology; the other is operation.
Socrates’ daimon and general daimonic ecology. Socrates is the exemplar, not the whole system.
Vocation/fate bridge and Apuleius’ own doctrine. Greenbaum belongs as later expansion, not as if Apuleius already gives horoscopic technique.

