Overlap warnings
Proclus vs Plotinus: Plotinus often feels like ascent-oriented metaphysical mysticism; Proclus is more systematic, hierarchical, and theologically plural.
Henads vs archetypes: do not psychologize them. Henads are divine unities, not inner moods.
Participation vs metaphor: participation is ontological sharing, not “reminds me of.”
Theurgy: Elements gives metaphysical scaffolding, not the full ritual theory. Bring in Proclus’ Timaeus Commentary or Platonic Theology later.
Proclus vs simple emanation: do not describe only downward emanation. The Proclean engine is remaining, procession, and return.
